Exercise
--------

Create a class "web" if file /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf exists.

Generate a report "I am a webserver" if the class "web" is true.


Bonus exercise
--------------

Create a class "TuesdayLinux" using the "expression" promise attribute 
that checks, on its right hand side, the hard classes "linux" AND
"Tuesday".

Generate a report if TuesdayLinux is set.
